ed in the literature, and suggests that the moderately high\ntemperatures needed for H-desorption result from slow kinetics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jul 2006 14:33:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2007 16:02:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
