onstrates the feasibility of quantum communication in\nspace, involving satellites or the International Space Station (ISS).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jul 2006 14:29:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Jul 2006 07:47:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-08-30"}
